title: Sibling Watchery - Drag Race UK Season 3 - Episode 2
description:
Bob and Monet review the second episode of Drag Race UK this season and they aren't holding back! Tune in to hear who they think are shaping up to be the top contenders, who they think the show will send home, and who needs to learn how to steam their look before stepping on the stage.
